room_title: Escape room "Nuclear Meltdown" by Baffled Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 7420 W. Cactus Road STE B12 Peoria, AZ 85381
room_description: You are the best and brightest the FBI has to offer and you have been called upon to unravel and decipher the code of a brilliant computer hacker. He has accessed the launch codes to an arsenal of nuclear warheads that are all aimed at the superpowers of the world. The launch is scheduled to start in an hour. Do you and a group of your peers have what it takes to stop the final countdown?
